java.lang.Object
  owltools.io.TableToAxiomConverter

public class TableToAxiomConverter
extends java.lang.Object

reads in a table (e.g. tab-delimited table) converting each row to an OWL Axiom. These could be ClassAssertion axioms, SubClassOf axioms, etc
